Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the rendezvous port!\NWhy hasn't anyone come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An incident had already taken place\Nthe night before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Number-One Samurai in the Land of Wano!\NHere comes Kozuki Oden!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:55.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,NIGHT BEFORE THE GREAT BATTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Akazaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to show you hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,BEACH OF KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--{\i1}Did you find the ship?{\i0}\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let them have their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, bridges!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,GREAT BRIDGE BETWEEN KIBI AND UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The great bridge between Kibi and Udon\Nhas been blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:11.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,GREAT BRIDGE BETWEEN KURI AND UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The great bridge between Kuri and Udon\Nhas been blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They had it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,GREAT BRIDGE BETWEEN RINGO AND HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!\NThe great bridge that connects the regions is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot get to the other side now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi-sama! All the ships \Nhave been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:33.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,ITACHI PORT, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is fine. We will rebuild \Nonce everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have not seen the Akazaya members\Nor samurai troops who they recruited with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People skipped forward in time\Nfrom 20 years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How can anyone believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless they see one of their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:05:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, even if they see it,\Nit is still hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that damn fool, Yasuie,\Nmade it sound even more ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But the information is credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akazaya members are alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not care if my men think\Nthat I am talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have authority to take action!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have blocked all the routes to Tokage Port.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:30.93,On Top,,0,0,0,,TOKAGE PORT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Four thousand troops?\NGood job recruiting so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one will make it to the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not give them even \Na chance to get revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you Akazaya ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallow in the despair from\Nbeing isolated and helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking that small boat is like suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's regroup and begin again\Nwhen we get another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we miss this opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to wait for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But we cannot hide anymore.\NThey will find out that we took control of Udon soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido's whole army will come to hunt rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot continue to steal \Ntheir food anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we left Kuri,\Nyou surely heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Okobore Town\Nwho were believed in our great battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...were burned alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...was my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow us to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want us to flee\Nand live in disgrace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to live with Hiyori-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your father had no support at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had not met Oden-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We would not be samurai\Nsince we were all immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we want to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...Oden-sama's samurai \Nretainers until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not go, Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not go!\NI do not want to lose even one more person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This centuries old national isolation\Nis deeply tied to Kozuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The time will eventually come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the world starts to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,open up the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forty one years ago, in the Flower Capital...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki Oden is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hide your wives!\N--And daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide the livestock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--He failed to set sail again!\N--He wants to get out of here that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was a very popular man in the capital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so restrictive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so restrictive\Nthat I might be squeezed to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come! Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to see the big world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops... I want to eat {\i1}oden{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A vast expanse of green forest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through flowers, plants, and trees that are growing thick,\Na fresh stream runs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And a beautiful sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a story that takes place in the Land of Wano\Nwhen it was still teeming with life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,TEAHOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You got away from a moving mountain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was groaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the mountain god became angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!\NAnyway, you all look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:46.89,On Top,,0,0,0,,MISS TSURU, WAITRESS AT \NTHE MOUNTAIN PASS TEAHOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What a splendid boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take it to the capital,\Nwe'll get one Platinum coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to build a decent house!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The Kurokoma boss is looking for\Na legendary white boar to display in his storefront,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so he posted a reward for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't display it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,White boars are divine messengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You stole money from our store again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:38.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,KIN'EMON - TOWN THUG
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tsuru!\NWe've known each other since childhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like your big brother\Nand I need money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you gamble!\NDo you know how much you owe me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time you put your hands on my money,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sell your organs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cannot pay me back,\Nleave all your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}KIN{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Tsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She really stripped me naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I got to hear a money-making idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.58,On Top,,0,0,0,,KATSUZO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Katsuzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.96,On Top,,0,0,0,,A CREMATORY, FLOWER CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a funeral so you get to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The cremation is finished,\Nso we were about to gather his bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We found him cooking {\i1}oden{\i0}\Nwith the flame that burned my father's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Oden-sama is \Nnot capable of sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his 38th attempt\Nto leave the country illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he return alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect you probably know,\Nbut let me tell you briefly of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,KOZUKI SUKIYAKI (ODEN'S FATHER)\NSHOGUN OF THE LAND OF WANO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was not even a year old yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he sent his nanny flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was two,\Nhe caught two rabbits at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was four, he threw a boulder\Nand knocked out a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was six, he spent all his time\Nat the pleasure hall wasting the castle's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was eight,\Nhe went to a gambling parlor by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and started a brawl\Nwith some hot-blooded gamblers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was nine, he was blacklisted by yakuza\Nand repaid them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...by setting their gambling parlor on fire,\Ninstigating a gang war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he got arrested for assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was at the age of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,While serving his time at quarries,\Nhe showed his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He even became a master stonemason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be in the Kozuki's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he came back on the street\Nas a better person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When Oden-sama was 14 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The capital suffered a drought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wells dried up\Nand he could not stand watching people suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So he changed the river's course\Nand made it flow to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it caused a massive flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And an arrest warrant was issued again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to flee from the country\Nthrough the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But he failed quite miserably!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when he was 15, he strong-armed\Na mountain temple master and stayed hidden there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought back women from the capital every night\Nand formed a harem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be some kind of monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I should add that\Nall those women were always free to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But some people became furious\Nand stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They were those women's boyfriends,\Nparents, and husbands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A group of strong samurai backed them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama welcomed their challenge\Nand fought back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what is known as the Harem War!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Hyogoro Family who tried to stop them\Ngot involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and a great scuffle took place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama is now 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He has made trouble at a steady pace up to today.\NThat is all I have to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not need your commentary,\Njust deliver this to Oden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:53.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,NOTICE OF DISAVOWAL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will break off my relationship with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time we drink together,\Nit'll be in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,FLOWER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'd excuse me,\Nladies and gentlemen of the bereaved family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? So cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the Oden \Nspeech people talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I am in luck.\NThis is like winning the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I give this to the Kurokoma boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Give me all your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa-whoa! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to get big money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!\NLet me go to the Kurokoma Family's mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that kid who stole our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch him and flay him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:16.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,HYOGORO THE FLOWER\NA YAKUZA OF THE CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But do not engage one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He is stronger than you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was entrusted with 60 Silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just use it, it'll be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have the smaller pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running an errand for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's 30 Silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Here you go.\N--Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bought the wrong pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed the bigger one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigger one is 60 Silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,60 SILVER COINS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already paid you 30 Silver coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so giving you this pot makes it 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat fooled that man\Nand saved 30 Silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:08.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,DENJIRO - AN ORPHAN IN THE CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Denjiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a pretty valuable thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like I really wanna arrest you,\Nso you can bribe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now why isn't everyone avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like all they care about is a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know it, Kin-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't bring that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You mean this white boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurokoma boss is trying to destroy the Hyogoro Family\Nby using it as a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean wherever that little boar is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,its parent boar will come \Ncharging any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Parent boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,According to an ancient document,\Nit's a massive white boar like a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they call it the mountain god!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One story tells that several centuries ago,\Nit destroyed the whole region in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was just a myth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...since the white boar really exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain god really exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll swallow us and kill us!\NIt's already right there! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! It's my fault that the capital is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an interesting conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...but give that white boar to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The daring Oden's unrivaled \Nstrength impresses Kin'emon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kin'emon pledges his loyalty to Oden\Nand they meet imperfect allies across the country!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oden and Akazaya Nine later become legend\Nin the Land of Wano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is how they began their \Nrollicking, vagrant journey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Tearfully Swearing Allegiance! Oden and Kin'emon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:49.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,